			<section class="about">
				<h1>About Course</h1>
				<div class="about-card">
					<p class="intro">
						Everything is designed.. Design 101 is a program created by Senpai
						to attract and impact as many people as we can with the basic
						knowledge of design.
					</p>
					<p class="main">
						This program spans 6 weeks and is open to both new and existing
						design enthusiasts who wish to improve their skills and join our
						community of creative technology talents. Times are changing and we
						as creative people need to equip ourselves with the skills needed to
						thrive in the new world. We are certain this course becomes the one
						thing that propels you on your journey to greater heights.
					</p>
